text: I had an incredible play in Grixis Clones last night.
I was behind, but had a far graveyard. My last opponent drops Scavenger Grounds but doesn't have the mana to activate it, passes turn.
I have mana to cast Sunbird's and Gary.
I cast Sunbird's. I cast Gary.
Gary hits Living Death.
Loving Death resolves before Gary. I have Massacre Wurm and about 6 clones in the yard. Now I have 7 Massacre Wurms. Gary resolves and drains 20 something.
I still lost, but it was an epic game.
Sweet!
